Description: Please see the review of my guitars recently sold. PRICE JUST REDUCED! This is my vintage Univox 335 in very nice condition. Someone will get a very well kept guitar. A few light scuffs here and there and a scratch mark on the back of the neck. The pickups have been tested as well as the wiring harness and all good to go. Buy with confidence.
